    "description": "Orlando the Fireman is a really simple game where you play as the title character trying to save as many lives you can from burning buildings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452860/extras/27838cd4044e37027134e8cf145c9821.poster.avif?t=1726326411\" width=600 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452860/extras/27838cd4044e37027134e8cf145c9821.webm?t=1726326411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452860/extras/27838cd4044e37027134e8cf145c9821.mp4?t=1726326411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452860/extras/433678216ceb64c6048dff7d147747ef.webp?t=1726326411\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br>Be the multitask hero saving many victims from 2 buildings at the same time while dodging big flames. Orlando will be continuously raised by the ladder between the buildings and you must click anywhere on the screen to switch the building he is facing. Choose the windows with the victims and avoid the burning ones until the water is ready.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452860/extras/99d12310a4ddc04aa667d3fff0fe1d3c.webp?t=1726326411\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452860/extras/27a3ffd69ecdca3c791a44e4e70a8b15.poster.avif?t=1726326411\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452860/extras/27a3ffd69ecdca3c791a44e4e70a8b15.webm?t=17263264